{"date":"1984-02-04","platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/f5/cb/37170_26Tsk.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/f5/cb/37170_26Tsk.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/f5/cb/37170_26Tsk.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/f5/cb/37170_26Tsk.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/f5/cb/37170_26Tsk.jpg"},"summary":"　　二重太陽サンズを取り巻く５つの惑星からなる太陽系ペンタゴナ・ワールド。その辺境にある惑星コアムに青雲の志を胸に故郷を旅立った若者２人、ダバ・マイロードとミラウー・キャオがいた。\r\n　　支配者ポセイダルによって治められているもののペンタゴナ・ワールドの政治は腐敗しており、各地では反乱軍が決起し戦乱が絶えなかった。ダバたちは元盗賊団のファンネリア・アムや、同様に青雲の志に燃えるギャブレット・ギャブレーと出会い、あるいは衝突しながら、ペンタゴナ・ワールドの実態を知るようになる。\r\n　　ヘビーメタル・エルガイムを駆り、ポセイダル軍と戦うダバは、やがて反乱軍のリーダーとなっていった。","name":"重戦機エルガイム","name_cn":"重战机艾尔盖姆","tags":[{"name":"富野由悠季","count":69,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":64,"total_cont":0},{"name":"SUNRISE","count":59,"total_cont":0},{"name":"萝卜","count":41,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1984","count":37,"total_cont":0},{"name":"永野护","count":33,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原创","count":27,"total_cont":0},{"name":"科幻","count":19,"total_cont":0},{"name":"机战","count":15,"total_cont":0},{"name":"北爪宏幸","count":11,"total_cont":0},{"name":"渡辺由自","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"永野護","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"战争","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"80年代","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1984年2月","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"サンライズ","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"robo","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1980s","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TVA","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"80s","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"年番","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1984年","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"80","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"机器人","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"4クール","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"電視","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"机甲","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"待补","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":